{
  "texts": [
    "Biological processes showing low or no expression in the analysed tissues of interest exhibited lower accuracy (e.g.",
    "bin-13.3 'Cell division.meiotic recombination'; average acc = 0.68) than those highly expressed (e.g.",
    "bin-2.3 'Cellular respiration.tricarboxylic acid cycle'; average acc = 0.87).",
    "The correlation between the average prediction accuracy and the average expression of functional categories reached Spearman's ⍴ = 0.76 and p value <2.2e-16.",
    "Finally, we tested the SSR models in terms of their prediction accuracy in species they were not trained on, in what we called a cross-species prediction (Fig. 2c, d)."
  ]
}